WEBVTT

00:00:00.788 --> 00:00:03.332
I have a death wish.

00:00:04.417 --> 00:00:09.422
Now before you just boo me off the stage
for saying such a thing in a pandemic,

00:00:09.422 --> 00:00:11.632
I'll explain with a little back story,

00:00:11.632 --> 00:00:14.552
starting with my second grade gym class.

00:00:14.594 --> 00:00:17.096
This was the longest,

00:00:17.096 --> 00:00:19.891
most humiliating hour of the week.

00:00:19.932 --> 00:00:24.312
My PE teacher, Mr. Jensen,
was a former drill sergeant,

00:00:24.353 --> 00:00:28.566
and I always felt like the weakest kid.

00:00:28.608 --> 00:00:29.734
On my report card,

00:00:29.776 --> 00:00:33.738
he checked the boxes corresponding
to what must have been important